com.rscja.deviceapi

Class RFIDWithLF

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.rscja.deviceapi.RFIDWithLF

  • public class RFIDWithLF
extends java.lang.Object
    RFID低频（125K）操作类
    RFID LF (125K) operation type

    注意：
    Attention:
    1、使用前请确认您的机器已安装此模块。
    1. Make sure this module is installed before using your device.
    2、要正常使用模块需要在\libs\armeabi\目录放置libDeviceAPI.so文件。
    2. Put libDeviceAPI.so file in directory \libs\armeabi\ then the module can be used normally.
    3、在操作设备前需要调用 init() 打开设备，使用完后调用 free() 关闭设备
    3. call init() to switch on the device before operating the device
    , call free() to switch off the device after using.

    Author:
    liuruifeng
